fields.name: Ben Dover
fields.description: A feathered diva with a passion for opera, often seen conducting symphonies with his tail feathers while channeling the grace of a lumbering bison.

fields.name: Peter Gosinya
fields.description: A finch with the illusion of a rockstar, regularly seen mistaking worm wriggles for wild mosh pits at sunup.

fields.name: Anita Bath
fields.description: This fastidious finch often found vigorously flapping in puddles, convinced she's a one-bird synchronized swim team.
